OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1774807892
OL,3,CCCTV captures hooded man smashing shop
OL,4,Cwindows with hammer
OL,6,FCCTV has captured the moment a hooded
OL,7,Fman smashed multiple shop windows with
OL,8,Fa hammer in a Kent town.
OL,10,FThe shop in New Romney, Drive Motor
OL,11,FSpares, was targeted last night
OL,12,F(Thursday 26 March).
OL,14,FThe owner, Ruth Shilling Jennings,
OL,15,Fsaid the damage is expected to cost
OL,16,Fmore than #30,000 to fix.
OL,18,FShe said: "It's really soul-
OL,19,Fdestroying, in a way, because we've
OL,20,Fspent so long trying to get this shop
OL,21,Fright.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1774807892
OL,3,CCCTV captures hooded man smashing shop
OL,4,Cwindows with hammer
OL,6,F"We've been on the high street for 15
OL,7,Fyears.
OL,9,F"We recently purchased this shop and
OL,10,Fmoved eight months ago and spent a lot
OL,11,Fof time and effort in doing it up and
OL,12,Frefurbishing it to the state that it
OL,13,Fis today and to have that then taken
OL,14,Faway.
OL,16,F"And it's a shame for the community as
OL,17,Fwell. They were so pleased when we
OL,18,Ffirst moved into the new shop and the
OL,19,Fresponse that we have had today,
OL,20,Fthey're gutted, everyone's gutted."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1774807892
OL,3,CCCTV captures hooded man smashing shop
OL,4,Cwindows with hammer
OL,6,FMrs Shilling Jennings said the
OL,7,Fcommunity have been left "shocked" but
OL,8,Fpeople have rallied together following
OL,9,Fthe attack.
OL,11,FShe said: "The community spirit that
OL,12,Fhas come out this morning.
OL,14,F"We've had so many people wanting to
OL,15,Fshare their footage from their
OL,16,Fdoorbell cameras, from their CCTV,
OL,17,Fringing up with information that they
OL,18,Ffeel might be helpful to the police
OL,19,Finquiry.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1774807892
OL,3,CCCTV captures hooded man smashing shop
OL,4,Cwindows with hammer
OL,6,F"It's been a real community support, a
OL,7,Freal spirit of the community, and
OL,8,Fthat's, I think, what we've taken away
OL,9,Ffrom this, that we're obviously valued
OL,10,Fand it's made us feel really nice in
OL,11,Fthe community, and that's what we're
OL,12,Fhere for."
OL,14,FThe team will be "resilient" and "get
OL,15,Fthrough it", she added.
OL,17,FHowever, this shop wasn't the only one
OL,18,Ftargeted last night.
OL,20,FThe funeral directors along the road
OL,21,Falso had its windows smashed.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1774807892
OL,3,CCCTV captures hooded man smashing shop
OL,4,Cwindows with hammer
OL,6,FJon Maguire, co-owner and director of
OL,7,FDearman Bartlett Independent Funeral
OL,8,FDirectors Ltd, said the new business
OL,9,Fhas been there for five months.
OL,11,FDamage is expected to cost #20,000 to
OL,12,Ffix.
OL,14,FHe said: "We've put everything heart
OL,15,Fand soul into this to look after
OL,16,Feveryone.
OL,18,F"Someone comes along and does this."
OL,20,FHe added that the "community has been
OL,21,Fabsolutely phenomenal".
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1774807892
OL,3,CCCTV captures hooded man smashing shop
OL,4,Cwindows with hammer
OL,6,F"Everyone's come out and been so
OL,7,Fhelpful, so nice.
OL,9,F"We've all come together. But it just
OL,10,Fmakes you feel... Kind of lets you
OL,11,Fdown a little bit in humanity."
OL,13,FIn a statement, Kent Police said it
OL,14,Freceived multiple reports of a
OL,15,Fdisturbance in High Street, New
OL,16,FRomney, shortly after 11pm on Thursday
OL,17,F26 March.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
