PN,41807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1774807892
OL,3,CCCTV captures hooded man smashing shop
OL,4,Cwindows with hammer
OL,6,FIt added: "It was reported that a man
OL,7,Fapproached the area and damage was
OL,8,Fcaused to premises before the man left
OL,9,Fthe scene on foot.
OL,11,F"Officers attended and initial
OL,12,Fenquiries were completed.
OL,14,F"An investigation is ongoing and
OL,15,Fanyone with relevant information, who
OL,16,Fhas not yet spoken to police, should
OL,17,Fcall 01843 222289 quoting 46/48375/26."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/8
